   - `materialize_to_graph()` and `_build_cohort_triples()` now pass
     `rule.id` to `CohortVocabulary.in_cohort(...)`. The membership
     triple's predicate is rule-scoped, and `delete_cohort_triples()`
     receives the same rule-scoped predicate so a re-materialise only
     wipes the rule's own membership rows (the URI-prefix branch
     already scoped by rule, but the predicate branch did not).
